DESCRIPTION:PURPOSE-DRIVEN RETIREMENT PLANNING with Joe Jordan\n\nAgency Solutions LIVE | Tuesday\, May 26\, 2026 | 1:00 PM Eastern\n\nJoe Jordan - former senior VP at MetLife\, presenter to 400\,000+ financial professionals\, author of Living a Life of Significance - joins Agency Network for an exclusive members-only conversation.\n\nHis presentation explains why financial planning is becoming more like life coaching\, the defining issue of the 21st century\, and the six retirement risks clients need help addressing: longevity\, market volatility\, safe withdrawal rate\, sequence of returns\, inflation\, and health.\n\nFree for Agency Network members. Hosted live on Microsoft Teams.\n\nJoin via Microsoft Teams:\nhttps://teams.microsoft.com/meet/220283480698470?p=888ZyluWc3sU2SW4R5\n\nMeeting ID: 220 283 480 698 470\nPasscode: Ec7nZ3Yd\n\nConnecting Agents - Inspiring Greatness\nAgency Network
